{
  "stem": "1183.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were not an individual, and that was the purpose of it, to deaden you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You were not an individual anymore too much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, I was not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was just 16 at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Right?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were tattooed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The woman made a little error there, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she did it over again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the children who were there from Philips, they were tattooed under their arms, in the-- in the-- in the inside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And remaining-- the children remained in Auschwitz till the end, because it was the Philips Group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because apparently we were considered, we were a labor force and of use to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's why they didn't do with us what they did with the other people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Part of our group remained in Birkenau for four days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After four days, that part of the group left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our group, including me, the rest remained in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were scared, because we thought we knew what was going to happen, and we saw it, and that is going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we, as far as I can recall, we didn't-- we stood on appell day and night, and whatever they wanted to, cold, and hungry, and ever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to do our business sometimes in the wheelbarrow, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [NON-ENGLISH] I remember one day that-- the only day I worked and that was they told us to carry bricks from someplace to the railroad.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On that day, I was very close to the crematorium and to the tower.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when the railroad arriving-- and it was in the summer, a Hungarian transport with people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there I saw with my own eyes the selection was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
